headline.main: HALIFAX 'ENVIES' WASTERS OF EGGS; ' No Such Surplus' at Home, He Says in Cleveland, Where More Women Picket

lead_paragraph: CLEVELAND, Nov. 5 -- Lord Halifax, the British Ambassador, came to Cleveland today, saw some more anti-war picketing, and said to a reporter who asked him about yesterday's throwing of eggs and tomatoes at him in Detroit:
